!! example

<<emoji error>>  error

<<emoji question>> question

; rocket
<<emoji>> default is rocket

; shower
<<emoji shower>> default is rocket

; traffic
<<emoji traffic>> default is rocket

; tada
<<emoji tada>> this is a tada emoji

<<emoji hourglass>> bingo

; list
<<emoji dot-list>> still can use bullets for symbol macro

<<emoji dot-status>> status

<<emoji bingo>> bingo

<<emoji menu>> menu

Inspired by latex emoji package [[latex-emoji|https://github.com/stone-zeng/latex-emoji]] and [[neotw/bullets]]

